{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a967d8987c","title":"在“百花学社”成立大会上的发言","origin":"北京大学社会主义思想教育委员会编印《北京大学右派分子反动言论汇集》，一九五七年十月。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c87c9e65ae","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":29,"articleId":"a967d8987c"}],"tags":[{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"19f3f1b8ea","name":"北京大学"},{"id":"5cd6c93a1b","name":"张丽中"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"56da19a5de","type":"title","text":"在“百花学社”成立大会上的发言","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a967d8987c"},{"id":"97390b4a31","type":"authors","text":"北京大学张景中","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a967d8987c"},{"id":"c8230b6904","type":"subtitle","text":"（张景中：北京大学数学系学生）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a967d8987c"},{"id":"8e3c1bb56d","type":"paragraph","text":"黑格尔、恩格斯两个都是死人，不好。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a967d8987c"},{"id":"5e968c8c55","type":"paragraph","text":"孔夫子、毛泽东是半死半活，也不好。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a967d8987c"},{"id":"1036b2b592","type":"paragraph","text":"有人主张“社会主义心理学社”","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a967d8987c"},{"id":"813b153f4d","type":"paragraph","text":"有人主张“百花学社”","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a967d8987c"},{"id":"b2f7f68fd5","type":"paragraph","text":"1．它包括了刚才别人说的全部优点，","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a967d8987c"},{"id":"3d01e889ef","type":"paragraph","text":"2．符合时代色彩，","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a967d8987c"},{"id":"bae1899e6d","type":"paragraph","text":"3．有青年人的色彩，对组织学社来说，还相当新鲜。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a967d8987c"},{"id":"867d7ec1fe","type":"paragraph","text":"4．是毛主席提出的。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a967d8987c"},{"id":"5f528a6e8e","type":"paragraph","text":"“学”已有思维之意，学而不思则殆。“社”就表示有组织。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a967d8987c"},{"id":"0a00653e55","type":"paragraph","text":"我们首先关心的主要是政治生活中的问题，作为学术问题讨论，方式应是自下而上，自上而下都可以。改革时，则是自上而下贯彻于领导。","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a967d8987c"},{"id":"075ac38a0c","type":"paragraph","text":"我们要使教条主义空气稀薄，使学术空气浓厚。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a967d8987c"},{"id":"4ba054cb41","type":"paragraph","text":"我们中间的意见可以充分发表，我对谭天荣的意见有80％的不同意，是形而上学的，但还是可以油印出来。","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a967d8987c"},{"id":"3e0334dfbc","type":"paragraph","text":"有人说，“人与人只有合作的关系，没有领导与被领导的关系。”我一般的说是不同意的。毛主席和党就可以领导我们，但学术性团体不要领导，也不要民主集中制，大家集体领导，不要什么组织纪律。","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a967d8987c"}],"page":{"id":"f67550d100","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a967d8987c","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}